text: R. Ecleo, Sr. is one of 14 Barangays of the municipality of Cagdianao, Dinagat Islands, Philippines, it is situated in the south portion of the province.R. Ecleo, Sr., Dinagat Islands - Google Maps ==Education== The barangay hosts the R.E. Ecleo Sr. Elementary School which was established, January 01, 1984R. Ecleo, Sr. Elementary School and the R. E. Ecleo Sr. National High School, established January 01, 2000R. E. Ecleo Sr. National High School. Both are part of the Dinagat Islands District. == References == == External links == * Province of Dinagat Islands - Official webpage * R. Ecleo, Sr. Elementary School * R. E.
